%% Diagram: Storage tiering lifecycle
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Hot: upload + transcode
    Hot --> Warm: views/day drops below threshold<br/>(typically after 30 days)
    Warm --> Cold: views/day approaches zero<br/>(typically after 90 days)
    Cold --> Archive: original raw bytes only<br/>(retention copy)
    Hot --> Hot: trending re-promote
    Warm --> Hot: rediscovered<br/>(viral re-share)
    Cold --> Hot: traffic spike<br/>(promote on miss)
    Cold --> [*]: deleted by lifecycle<br/>(zero views > 365 days)
